{"tid":2384013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"通訊局再裁定三集《頭條新聞》辱警「驚訊」主持從垃圾桶冒出　暗示警員遭人厭惡唾棄","createTime":"2021-01-28T09:42:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T11:02:46.000Z","uid":22556,"like":11,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"3d89fd4760be33fddd61a7a6d0cfe89245f467a7","tid":2384013,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T09:42:50.000Z","msg":"通訊局去年裁定《頭條新聞》其中一集「驚方訊息」（驚訊）環節內容辱警，環節隨即被腰斬。通訊局今（ 28 日）再裁定多三集《頭條》污衊和侮辱警員，向港台發出強烈勸諭。通訊局指，三集「驚訊」環節開始時，主持人王喜均裝扮成警員，以垃圾膠袋裹着頸和雙手，開場時從垃圾桶冒出，「暗示警務人員均被視為廢物，遭人厭惡唾棄」，認為屬惡意描繪。<br />\n<br />\n通訊局又指，其中一集「驚訊」播出葵青警區指揮官謝振中在區議會發言片段，畫面加上「FAKE NEWS／謊言」標題，令人覺得謝說謊和製造假新聞，導致他聲譽受損，但未有向謝提供機會回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%80%9A%E8%A8%8A%E5%B1%80%E5%86%8D%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%89%E9%9B%86-%E9%A0%AD%E6%A2%9D%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E-%E8%BE%B1%E8%AD%A6-%E9%A9%9A%E8%A8%8A-%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81%E5%BE%9E%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E6%A1%B6%E5%86%92%E5%87%BA-%E6%9A%97%E7%A4%BA%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E9%81%AD%E4%BA%BA%E5%8E%AD%E6%83%A1%E5%94%BE%E6%A3%84/?fbclid=IwAR2zcWBdw1kshadwqkH_oQ0zXrofVt945p4VigEWXdOGYJcRtvERKnhNX4s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25A8%258A%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%25AE%259A%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%259B%2586-%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%25A2%259D%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E-%25E8%25BE%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E9%25A9%259A%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%25BE%259E%25E5%259E%2583%25E5%259C%25BE%25E6%25A1%25B6%25E5%2586%2592%25E5%2587%25BA-%25E6%259A%2597%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E9%2581%25AD%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258E%25AD%25E6%2583%25A1%25E5%2594%25BE%25E6%25A3%2584%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2zcWBdw1kshadwqkH_oQ0zXrofVt945p4VigEWXdOGYJcRtvERKnhNX4s&d=YX1qj72dVL8lCt3J0nVEUtVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=9101bbb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25A8%258A%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%2586%2